hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 相关方程：
   $$L(M_c)=L_{ref}\Bigl(\frac{M_c}{M_{ref}}\Bigr)^\alpha,\qquad L=q_{He}\frac{dM_c}{dt}.$$
2. 表达 $\frac{dM_c}{dt}$：
   $$\frac{dM_c}{dt}=\frac{L}{q_{He}}
   =\frac{L_{ref}}{q_{He}}\Bigl(\frac{M_c}{M_{ref}}\Bigr)^\alpha.$$
3. 分离变量并从 $M_{c,i}$ 到 $M_{c,f}$ 积分：
   $$dt=\frac{q_{He}}{L_{ref}}M_{ref}^\alpha M_c^{-\alpha}\,dM_c,$$
   $$\tau_{He}=\int_{0}^{\tau_{He}}dt
   =\frac{q_{He}M_{ref}^\alpha}{L_{ref}}\int_{M_{c,i}}^{M_{c,f}}M_c^{-\alpha}\,dM_c.$$
4. 使用 $\int M_c^{-\alpha}dM_c=\frac{M_c^{\,1-\alpha}}{1-\alpha}$ 进行积分：
   $$\tau_{He}
   =\frac{q_{He}M_{ref}^\alpha}{L_{ref}}
   \left[\frac{M_c^{\,1-\alpha}}{1-\alpha}\right]_{M_{c,i}}^{M_{c,f}}
   =\frac{q_{He}M_{ref}^\alpha}{L_{ref}(1-\alpha)}
   \bigl(M_{c,f}^{\,1-\alpha}-M_{c,i}^{\,1-\alpha}\bigr).$$
5. 将分母改写为 $(\alpha-1)$：
   $$\tau_{He}
   =\frac{q_{He}M_{ref}^\alpha}{L_{ref}(\alpha-1)}
   \bigl(M_{c,i}^{\,1-\alpha}-M_{c,f}^{\,1-\alpha}\bigr).$$
